を生成します。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>new RangeError([<var>message</var>[, <var>fileName</var>[, <var>lineNumber</var>]]])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\"><code><var>message</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>人間が読むためのエラーの説明です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename\"><code><var>fileName</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>例外が発生したコードを含むファイルの名前です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"linenumber\"><code><var>lineNumber</var></code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>例外が発生したコードの行番号です。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_rangeerror_for_numeric_values","title":"RangeError の使用 (数値)","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">500</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">500</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RangeError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"The argument must be between -500 and 500.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">try</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RangeError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Handle the error</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_rangeerror_for_non-numeric_values","title":"RangeError の使用 (数値以外)","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"apple\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"banana\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"carrot\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RangeError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The argument must be an \"apple\", \"banana\", or \"carrot\".'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">try</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cabbage\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RangeError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Handle the error</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"http